As a user, I want the system to analyze my past meal choices and consumption patterns to provide insights on my eating habits, nutritional intake, and areas for improvement. 
As a user with varying levels of cooking expertise, I want the system to provide clear and easy-to-follow recipes, along with instructional videos or tutorials for complex dishes. 
As a user, I want the ability to customize my preferences and dietary restrictions so that the system can provide tailored recommendations and meal plans that align with my needs.
